title: D-Man's Weekly Vent:  Weeden Set To Fail In Big D
content:
Dennis Manoloff of the Cleveland Plain Dealer joined Baskin & Phelps Friday to discuss Brandon Weeden's chances of success leading the Dallas Cowboys this upcoming weekend, if the boo birds will rain down on Josh McCown if he struggles against Oakland, the mistaken report on Tristan Thompson's negotiations, and more.
